column5: Can i get maps on line? I need 6216,6286 and 6287. I would like the new one for LOTW.

I have ordered all my Canadian maps from the Hudson Map Company.Not sure if you can order them online, but give them a call and they will ship direct.www.hudsonmap.comHudson Map Company2510 Nicollet AvenueMinneapolis, MN 55404tel: 612-872-8818fax: 612-872-1855Toll free: 1-800-473-1412
Canada Map Sales 877-627-7226, but be sure to ask them to use a heavy duty shipping tube or it may arrive damaged and creased.
Try this link. I have ordered from them, they are fast and reliable. Make sure you get the new foldable wateproof maps. They are great.http://www.maptown.com/index.html
